Event Title: Invitation to Discuss Regular Speaker Series at CMU-SV | Swartz
Description:
Dear All,

I hope this email finds you well. I wanted to extend my gratitude for your agreement to meet with Namrata, a representative from Swartz, at the CMU SV campus.

The purpose of the meeting is to discuss the possibility of establishing a regular speaker series at CMU-SV. Our goal is to bring in experts in various fields to share their knowledge and insights with the community.

The meeting will be held in-person, and I kindly ask that you let me know if your availability changes in the meantime.

Thank you for your time and I look forward to seeing you at the meeting.

Best Regards,Navtej
